Pick up a knife out of the sink.
Turn around and carry the knife to the table.
Cut the bread sitting on the table.

Drop the knife into the sink.

Pick up a piece of bread from the table.

Pick up the sharp knife from the sink.
Turn and carry the knife to the brown table next to the wall.
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the table.
Turn and carry the knife to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and move back to the table with the sliced tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Carry the slice of tomato across the room to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato on the second shelf on the right and then remove after a few seconds.
Carry the slice of tomato to the counter above the dishwasher and left of the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink to the left of the sharp knife.

Grab the knife out of the sink
Turn around and head to the right side of the table
Cut the tomato on the table into slices
Turn around and head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn around and head to the tomato on the table
Grab one of the tomato slices on the table
Turn left and head to the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge. Close the fridge. Then take the tomato out of the fridge
Turn around and head to the sink

Take the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the wood table.
Cut the tomato on the wood table into slices.

Put the knife into the sink.
Turn around and walk to the wood table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left, then right and walk around the table, turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the tomato slice in the refrigerator and close the door, open the door and remove the tomato slice.
